Package: gamezoneR
Type: Package
Title: Acquiring and Analyzing STATS LLC's GameZone College Basketball Data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person('Jack', 'Lichtenstein', email = 'jacklich10@gmail.com', role = c('aut','cre'))
Maintainer: Jack Lichtenstein <jacklich10@gmail.com>
Description:  Provides numerous utilities for acquiring and analyzing
    NCAA Men's Basketball play-by-play data from GameZone <http://gamezone.stats.com/>.
    The package allows users to scrape team and master schedules as well as
    play-by-play data with shot locations into a tidy format.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/JackLich10/gamezoneR, http://gamezoner.sportsdataverse.org/
BugReports: https://github.com/JackLich10/gamezoneR/issues
